    "title": "Fast & Convenient Car Rental at 1,500+ Locations | National Car Rental",
    "author": null,
    "publish_date": null,
    "main_content": "National Car Rental offers fast and convenient car rental at 1,500+ locations worldwide. Join Emerald Club and enjoy exclusive benefits including counter bypass, choose your own car and earn rewards towards free rental days at select locations. Emerald Club members get on their way faster with a faster, more convenient experience every time they rent a vehicle. The Emerald Club is designed to make your car rental experience faster and more convenient, with special privileges reserved for frequent renters. Services include bypassing the counter, choosing your own vehicle from a sporty Midsize to something more rugged, and turning business trips into free rental days. National promises to put you first with exceptional customer service and vehicles that are maintained and cleaned to high-quality standards through their Standard of Care commitment.",
    "with": [
      "National Car Rental has worldwide locations in the United States, Canada, Europe, Latin America, the Caribbean, Asia-Pacific, Africa and Australia.",
      "Emerald Club members get on their way, faster with a faster, more convenient experience every time you rent a vehicle.",
